</P>
<P>
 A "Valentine Interlude" menu is planned for Friday and Monday evenings at 
Nostrum Mare Bistro. 
</P>
<P>
 The prix fixe dinner is $29 per person, plus tax and tip, and it includes a 
choice of entree: poached lobster Valentine, grilled pave of tenderloin and 
duck confit , roast game hen, or veal chop mallorca . Appetizer, salad and soup 
are served as well, and dessert is chocolate amore -- chocolate hearts layered 
with chocolate cream, berries and mascarpone sorbet, surrounded by passion 
fruit coulis . Dinner hours are 5 to 10 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 At the Doubletree Hotel, 100 The City Drive, Orange. (714) 634-4500. 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 In case you and your loved one like to laugh, Raffaello Ristorante will 
feature stand-up comedy in its lounge from 8:30 to 9:30 p.m. Friday through 
Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 The restaurant's Valentine menu includes such dishes as chicken with 
mascarpone cheese and radicchio, agnello al rosmarino , and white chocolate 
souffle. 
</P>
<P>
 The price is $29.50 per person, plus tax and tip. Dinner is served from 5 to 
10 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 1998 N. Tustin Ave., Orange. (714) 283-8230. 
