<P>
 In the Pacific Coast League: 
</P>
<P>
 Estancia 55, Century 52 (OT) -- Clay Frenz scored with 12 seconds left in 
overtime for host Estancia (15-9, 6-3), which cliched a playoff berth. Frenz, 
who had 17 points, sent the game into overtime with a three-pointer with three 
seconds left in regulation. Thomas Harmon scored 14 points for No. 6 Century 
(21-4, 7-2). 
</P>
<P>
 Laguna Beach 72, Costa Mesa 62 -- Five players scored in double figures for 
Laguna Beach (6-17, 2-7), which led 30-23 at halftime. 
