 Cerritos 7, Ventura 6 -- The Pirates (1-1) committed seven errors and lost the 
nonconference game. Cerritos catcher Dusty Wathan, son of former major leaguer 
John Wathan, went two for four, including the game-winning RBI in the seventh 
inning. 
