<DOCID> 012036 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 10, 1994, Thursday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Ventura County Life; Part J; Page 30 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
