<DOCNO> LA021094-0141 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 012043 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 10, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 1; Column 2; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
