Corp. Forest Lawn Mortuary, Hollywood Hills.  
</P>
<P>
 Mills, Gloria K., 71, of Burbank, homemaker. Eckerman-Heisman Funeral Service, 
Burbank.  
</P>
<P>
 Murphy, Gary L., 35, of Arleta, truck driver. Aftercare California Cremation & 
Burial Society, Van Nuys.  
</P>
<P>
 St. Angelo, Felix N., 78, of Glendale, retired bartender. Eckerman-Heisman 
Funeral Service, Burbank.  
</P>
<P>
 Velasquez, Martin, 88, of Chatsworth, retired custodian for Los Angeles 
Unified School District. Aftercare California Cremation & Burial Society, Van 
Nuys.  
</P>
<P>
 Voss, Shirley Lorraine, 63, of Granada Hills, homemaker. San Fernando 
Mortuary, San Fernando.  
</P>
