other things -- whether McDougal improperly diverted funds from Madison 
Guaranty Savings & Loan Assn., which he controlled, to Whitewater and Clinton 
gubernatorial campaigns. 
</P>
<P>
 Clark said the firm has kept documents, "in anticipation they will be 
requested." 
