<P>
 The California School Boards Assn. has named Assemblywomen Hilda L. Solis 
(D-EL Monte) as its outstanding freshman legislator for 1993. Last year, Solis 
co-authored several bills handling primary and secondary education, including 
AB-160, a bill giving additional money to school districts with decreased 
funding due to military base closures. 
</P>
