COMMUNITY NEWS / REGION: 5 WESTSIDE AGENCIES RECEIVE UNITED WAY QUAKE AID 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The United Way of Greater Los Angeles has raised $928,000 for earthquake 
relief, donating $73,800 of the sum to five Westside agencies. 
</P>
<P>
 New Directions on La Cienega Boulevard, T.H.E. Clinic for Women in Crenshaw, 
