<P>
 The Azusa Pacific women's basketball team entered the week with a five-game 
winning streak after defeating Southern California College, 73-70, in a Golden 
State Athletic Conference game Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
 Jessica Opfar scored 22 points for the Cougars (16-7). PREP OF THE WEEK 
</P>
