COMMUNITY NEWS: REGION: STATE PTA OFFERING COLLEGE SCHOLARSHIPS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By LISA RICHARDSON 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The California PTA is offering 100 scholarships to high school seniors for the 
fall semester or quarter at any accredited college or university in the state. 
</P>
<P>
 Students who have been volunteers in their schools or communities will be 
eligible for the $400 scholarships. Also, one $300 graphic arts scholarship 
will be available to a senior planning to enroll in the art department of an 
accredited art institution or college in California. 
</P>
<P>
 Applications are available at most high schools or from the state PTA office, 
P.O. Box 15015, Los Angeles, CA 90015. The deadline for applications is March 
15. LISA RICHARDSON 
