COMMUNITY NEWS: RANCHO PALOS VERDES: CITY HALL NEWS; RESIDENTS TO BE NAMED TO 
ADVISORY BOARDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By SUSAN WOODWARD 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The City Council will vote on public nominations for committee positions at a 
meeting Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
 Appointees will serve on volunteer advisory boards on traffic, parks and 
recreation, view restoration, finance and other committees. 
</P>
